</ul>\n</div><!--/TopicPath-->\n\n    <div class=\"recruit_nav_widget widget_place_01\">\n\t\t\t\n  <div class=\"inner_02\">\n    <nav>\n      <ul class=\"recruit_nav_list\">\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">採用情報TOP</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">仕事・人を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/environment/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">働く環境を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/application/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">募集要項</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/faq/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">採用Q&A</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/userfiles/files/recruit/panf_2026s.pdf\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\"target=\"_blank\">パンフレット</a></li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n    <div class=\"bg_01 recruit_top_area_01\">\n      <div class=\"inner_02\">\n        <h2 class=\"recruit_top_ttl\">「人財は最大の財産である」<br>という信念があります。</h2>\n        <p>沖縄日立ネットワークシステムズは沖縄のIT産業に貢献し、世界へも目を向けられる人財を求めています。高度な技術や知識の習得だけでなく、多角的な人財育成を行っているのが特徴のひとつでもあります。私たちの理念に賛同し目的の実現に向けて一緒に歩んでいける方、是非いっしょに沖縄日立ネットワークシステムズで働きましょう！</p>\n      </div>\n<div class=\"tac mgt60\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PrW9cJ7IGPY\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/youtube_mv2.jpg\" alt=\"OHNSのyoutubeチャンネルはこちら\" width=\"600\"></a></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"recruit_top_interview_outer\">\n      <section class=\"common_wide_content_layout_01\">\n        <div class=\"info_block_01 inner_01\">\n          <h2 class=\"top_lead_01\">Interview<span class=\"lead_txt_02\">仕事・人を知る</span></h2>\n          <a href=\"/recruit/interview/\" class=\"btn_01\">仕事・人を知る一覧</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info_block_02\">\n          <div class=\"inner_02\">\n            <div class=\"marker_txt\"><mark>会社の先輩たちへ仕事や会社について聞いたインタビュー集です。</mark></div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_outer\">\n            \n            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide\">\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview15/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_16.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:15\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:15</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2003年経験者採用<br />\r\n部署： 総務部　人事総務グループ</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview15/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview14/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_15.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:14\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:14</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 1999年10月<br />\r\n部署： コンタクトセンタ部　管理職</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview14/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview13/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_13.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:13\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:13</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2000年4月<br />\r\n部署： ソリューションビジネス第1部　管理職</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview13/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview12/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_12.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:12\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:12</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2018年1月<br />\r\n部署： 経理部　経理グループ</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview12/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview11/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_11.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:11\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:11</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2000年4月<br />\r\n部署： 営業部　営業グループ</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview11/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview10/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_10.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:10\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:10</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2005年4月<br />\r\n部署： サポートビジネス部</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview10/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview09/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_09.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:09\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:09</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2021年1月<br />\r\n部署： ソリューションビジネス第2部</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview09/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview08/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_08.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:08\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:08</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2002年4月<br />\r\n部署： コンタクトセンタ部</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview08/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview07/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_01.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:07\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:07</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2022年4月<br />\r\n部署： サポートビジネス部</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview07/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview06/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_02.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:06\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:06</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2021年４月<br />\r\n部署： コンタクトセンタ部</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview06/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview05/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_03.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:05\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:05</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 2013年4月<br />\r\n部署： ソリューションビジネス第1部</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview05/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview04/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_04.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:04\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:04</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社：2000年4月<br />\r\n部署：ソリューションビジネス第1部　管理職</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview04/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview03/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_05.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:03\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:03</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 1999年11月<br />\r\n部署： ソリューションビジネス本部　管理職</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview03/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview02/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_06.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:02\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:02</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 1999年10月<br />\r\n部署： サービスビジネス本部　管理職</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview02/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_item\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_img_block\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview01/\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/interview/tmb_07.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"225\" alt=\"Interview:01\"></a></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_name\">Interview:01</div>\n                <p class=\"recruit_interview_txt\">入社： 1999年10月<br />\r\n部署： 経営サポート本部　管理職</p>\n                <div class=\"recruit_interview_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/interview01/\" class=\"recruit_interview_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n              </div>\n                          </div>\n            <div class=\"recruit_interview_slide_append_arrows\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_outer\">\n      <div class=\"bg_content top_ourfield_bg\"></div>\n      <section class=\"common_wide_content_layout_01\">\n        <div class=\"info_block_01 inner_01\">\n          <h2 class=\"top_lead_01\">Our Field<span class=\"lead_txt_02\">働く環境を知る</span></h2>\n          <a href=\"/recruit/environment/\" class=\"btn_01\">働く環境を知る</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info_block_02\">\n          <div class=\"inner_02\">\n            <div class=\"marker_txt\"><mark>充実した福利厚生やキャリアパス、特に力を入れている社員への研修・教育体制について。</mark></div>\n            <div class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_item_outer\">\n              <ul class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_list\">\n                <li class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_item\">\n                  <div class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_img_block\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/img_02.jpg\" width=\"280\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                  <div class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_name\">福利厚生</div>\n                  <p class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_txt\">各種保険や休暇制度、社内イベントなど当社の福利厚生について。</p>\n                  <div class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/environment/welfare/\" class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n                </li>\n                                <li class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_item\">\n                  <div class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_img_block\"><img src=\"/userfiles/images/recruit/img_04.jpg\" width=\"280\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                  <div class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_name\">研修・教育</div>\n                  <p class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_txt\">グループ合同の新人導入技術教育、階層別教育など日立グループならではの教育システムを導入しています。</p>\n                  <div class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_link_txt\"><a href=\"/recruit/environment/training/\" class=\"recruit_top_ourfield_link\">詳細を見る</a></div>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"recruit_application_area\">\n      <div class=\"inner_02\">\n        <div class=\"info_block_01\">\n          <h2 class=\"top_lead_01\">Recruitment<span class=\"lead_txt_02\">募集要項</span></h2>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"info_block_02\">\n          <ul class=\"application_link_list\">\n            <li class=\"application_link_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/application/gurad/\" class=\"application_link\"><span class=\"application_name\">新卒者</span>採用</a></li>\n            <li class=\"application_link_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/application/career/\" class=\"application_link\"><span class=\"application_name\">経験者</span>採用</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"faq_area\">\n      <div class=\"inner_02 common_wide_content_layout_01\">\n        <div class=\"info_block_01\">\n          <h2 class=\"top_lead_01\">FAQ<span class=\"lead_txt_02\">採用Q&A</span></h2>\n                  </div>\n        <div class=\"info_block_02\">\n          <div class=\"list_faq\">\n            \n                        <div class=\"item\" id=\"faq_00073\">\n              <h3 class=\"btn_q\"><span data-href=\"0\">文系学部なのですが応募は可能ですか？</span></h3>\n              <div class=\"box_a\">\n                可能です。<br />\r\n文系学生の皆さんでも、ITに何かしら興味がある方であれば歓迎です。<br />\r\n興味だけでなく、「興味があってこんなことを勉強してます」等の明確な過程のある方は大歓迎！\n              </div>\n            </div>\n                        <div class=\"item\" id=\"faq_00074\">\n              <h3 class=\"btn_q\"><span data-href=\"1\">資格は取っておいた方が有利ですか？</span></h3>\n              <div class=\"box_a\">\n                有利です。<br />\r\n就職活動において、どの業界、職種においても有利な資格はあると思います。<br />\r\n当社の場合、技術系で入社する皆さんには、国家資格の「基本情報技術者」を推奨しております。\n              </div>\n            </div>\n                        <div class=\"item\" id=\"faq_00075\">\n              <h3 class=\"btn_q\"><span data-href=\"2\">育児休暇制度について教えてください。</span></h3>\n              <div class=\"box_a\">\n                育児だけでなく介護も制度があります。<br />\r\n制度の利用実績もあり、育児については、男性の利用実績もあります。<br />\r\n皆さん復帰もしておりますので、育児や介護しながら勤務する環境は整っている企業であると自負しております。\n              </div>\n            </div>\n                        <div class=\"item\" id=\"faq_00076\">\n              <h3 class=\"btn_q\"><span data-href=\"3\">将来のビジョンについて教えてください。</span></h3>\n              <div class=\"box_a\">\n                 当社は、設立以来、ソフトウェアの開発を中心とし拡大してきましたが、最近ではサポート系の事業も成長しており、 製品を「製造からサポート、保守まで」一貫して対応するノウハウが蓄積してきたと感じております。<br />\r\n今以上に技術力の幅を広げて、沖縄のIT産業にさらなる貢献を！　と思ってます。\n              </div>\n            </div>\n                      </div>\n\n          \n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"recruit_nav_widget widget_place_02\">\n\t\t\t\n  <div class=\"inner_02\">\n    <nav>\n      <ul class=\"recruit_nav_list\">\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">採用情報TOP</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/interview/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">仕事・人を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/environment/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">働く環境を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/application/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">募集要項</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/recruit/faq/\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\">採用Q&A</a></li>\n        <li class=\"recruit_nav_item\"><a href=\"/userfiles/files/recruit/panf_2026s.pdf\" class=\"recruit_nav_link\"target=\"_blank\">パンフレット</a></li>\n      </ul>\n    </nav>\n  </div>\n</div>\n  </main>\n  <!-- //pagebody --> \n\n  <!-- site_footer --> \n  <div id=\"FooterArea\">\n  <!-- コンテナ（幅1275px、レスポンシブ対応の場合）※「5. コンテナについて」を参照 -->\n  <div class=\"Container Wide\">\n    <a href=\"#top\" id=\"FooterPageTop\" aria-label=\"ページの先頭へ\"></a>\n    <!-- オプショナルフッタ 「7.3. オプショナルフッタ」を参照-->\n    <div id=\"Footer2\">\n            <!-- オプショナルフッタ項目「7.5. オプショナルフッタ項目」を参照 -->\n      <div id=\"Footer2Menu\">\n        <a href=\"/sitemap/\">サイトマップ</a>\n        <a href=\"/topics/\">新着情報</a>\n        <a href=\"/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- フッタ -->\n    <div id